{"tid":474864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"考車.","createTime":"2017-11-20T14:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T08:05:29.000Z","uid":80720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d60184fb93c97054d6e3eda7778f48e7591a3880","tid":474864,"uid":80720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T14:29:09.000Z","msg":"考左2次（棍）都肥<br />\n2次都係大tick 超越物體 未能注意路面狀況<br />\n呢個到底係咩意思<br />\n自問擰足頭 佢話未足我心服..<br />\n朋友就話可能過死車未夠一米<br />\n咁我要過一米 就要過雙白<br />\n咁我心諗過雙白實肥啦 所以我貼雙白<br />\n但又未夠一米 就係肥我呢樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我可以點做 求賜廢<br />\n準備再花彈藥黎多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426a19bbefc44d0cffdb6542d0de913995dd2734","tid":474864,"uid":80720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T14:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考左2次（棍）都肥<br />\n2次都係大tick 超越物體 未能注意路面狀況<br />\n呢個到底係咩意思<br />\n自問擰足頭 佢話未足我心服..<br />\n朋友就話可能過死車未夠一米<br />\n咁我要過一米 就要過雙白<br />\n咁我心諗過雙白實肥啦 所以我貼雙白<br />\n但又未夠一米 就係肥我呢樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我可以點做 求賜<strong>教</strong><br />\n準備再花彈藥黎多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8ec0c8f98d6eb3c6a11953fb807f06f12a3d5f43","tid":474864,"uid":121705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T14:38:33.000Z","msg":"有冇超越物體前減速，打燈，望對頭車先過？"},{"pid":"1288c6ea701572d1b93b4ec8d9c1326103e963dc","tid":474864,"uid":80720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇超越物體前減速，打燈，望對頭車先過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前面有紅van係左線<br />\n打燈 打燈擰頭 對面好後先有私家車<br />\n我後面冇車 咁我過完 打返左燈<br />\n照直行 <br />\n咁到底錯左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8758a42d94283ed63df4d92cb2f1f3f8b29dbfc0","tid":474864,"